name: Shania Twain (2000s)
description:
A commission of @Zorglub.

Shania Twain is a Canadian singer and actress known as the Queen of Country Pop. She's one of the best selling musicians of all time and a winner of 5 Grammy Awards.

(Update: Kept training the model and testing some steps, and 1800 seems better than the previous one I uploaded, so here it is.)

1800-step TI trained on a dataset of 18 images with my usual settings.

Appreciate my work? My TIs are free, but you can always buy me a coffee. :)

Curious about my work process? I have summarized it here.

How to create a good prompt using my TIs

You're obviously free to experiment, but bear in mind that my TIs are trained with a more or less fixed phrasing, that normally starts with:

"photo of EMBEDDING_NAME, a woman"

So I recommend always starting your prompt like that and then building the rest of the prompt from there. For instance, "photo of (shtw41n:0.99), a woman, RAW, close portrait photo, leopard print suit with hood, leopard print top, pale skin, slim body, (high detailed skin:1.2), 8k uhd, dslr, soft lighting, high quality, film grain, Fujifilm XT3 sharp focus, f 5.6, redhead, (hood on:1.2)".
